        <section id="living-room">
            <h2>Living Room</h2>
            <p>Transform your living room into a cozy and stylish space with these tips:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Color Scheme:</strong> Choose a calming color palette to make the space inviting.</li>
                <li><strong>Furniture Arrangement:</strong> Arrange furniture to create a conversation-friendly layout.</li>
                <li><strong>Lighting:</strong> Use a mix of ambient, task, and accent lighting to set the mood.</li>
                <li><strong>Decor Elements:</strong> Add personal touches with artwork, plants, and cushions.</li>
            </ul>
            <p><a href="#bathroom">Next: Bathroom Tips</a></p>
        </section>
        <section id="bathroom">
            <h2>Bathroom</h2>
            <p>Upgrade your bathroom decor with these practical and chic ideas:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Storage Solutions:</strong> Maximize space with stylish storage options.</li>
                <li><strong>Color and Texture:</strong> Use light colors and varied textures for a fresh look.</li>
                <li><strong>Lighting:</strong> Install bright, natural lighting to enhance the space.</li>
                <li><strong>Accessories:</strong> Add elegant accessories like mirrors, rugs, and towels.</li>
            </ul>
            <p><a href="#kitchen">Next: Kitchen Tips</a></p>
        </section>
        <section id="kitchen">
            <h2>Kitchen</h2>
            <p>Create a functional and beautiful kitchen with our expert tips:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Layout:</strong> Design an efficient layout for cooking and entertaining.</li>
                <li><strong>Cabinetry:</strong> Choose stylish and practical cabinetry for storage.</li>
                <li><strong>Lighting:</strong> Incorporate task lighting for work areas and ambient lighting for dining.</li>
                <li><strong>Decor:</strong> Personalize your kitchen with artwork and plants.</li>
            </ul>
            <p><a href="#bedroom">Next: Bedroom Tips</a></p>
        </section>
        <section id="bedroom">
            <h2>Bedroom</h2>
            <p>Design a serene and stylish bedroom with our advice:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Color Palette:</strong> Choose soothing colors to create a restful atmosphere.</li>
                <li><strong>Bedding:</strong> Invest in high-quality bedding for comfort and style.</li>
                <li><strong>Furniture:</strong> Select multifunctional furniture to maximize space.</li>
                <li><strong>Accessories:</strong> Add personal touches with artwork, rugs, and lamps.</li>
            </ul>
            <p><a href="#living-room">Back to Living Room Tips</a></p>
        </section>
